  "description": "Additive (Voice 1) meets Noise (Voice 2) at HAMMER +0.3 — light LOVE. The additive voice provides precise harmonic tones; the noise voice adds the electromagnetic interference of deep water. Sample-and-Hold LFO on Voice 2 creates unpredictable noise bursts that blend with the tonal foundation through LOVE's spectral merge. AMPULLAE at 1.0 — maximum sensitivity. Every slight velocity change reshapes the balance between signal and static. The hammerhead's ampullae detecting faint electrical signals in the dark.",
